 [Dependencies::Runtime::Removed]
 - Dist::Zilla::Plugin::KwaliteeTests
 - Dist::Zilla::Plugin::CriticTests

1.0.16 2011-08-28T07:59:59Z
 [Dependencies::Build::Removed]
 - English

 [Dependencies::Runtime::New]
